		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Whistling, you call forth heavy snowfall for a moment in an area, pelting creatures with snow.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save dex]]{Dexterity Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d6 bludgeoning]] damage and [[/damage 1d6 cold]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area is covered with snow and counts as &amp;reference[difficult terrain]. This difficult terrain is removed if any amount of it comes into contact with rain or fire damage.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> You target an additional 5 ft. radius area when you reach 5th level (2 areas), 11th level (3 areas), and 17th level (4 areas). Targets only roll the save once if the areas overlap.</p>",
